### 21 - VPN Client

Please follow Microsoft's instructions for installing the VPN Client for your operating system.

As well, tips and commands for using az and wget are given below.

**_References:_**

* [https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/vpn-gateway/point-to-site-vpn-client-configuration-azure-cert](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/vpn-gateway/point-to-site-vpn-client-configuration-azure-cert)


#### 21.1 - Verify VPN Client Configuration URL (amd64)


**_References:_**

* [https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/network/vnet-gateway/vpn-client?view=azure-cli-latest#az_network_vnet_gateway_vpn_client_generate](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/network/vnet-gateway/vpn-client?view=azure-cli-latest#az_network_vnet_gateway_vpn_client_generate)


**_Command(s):_**

```bash
export ARO_VGW_CONFIGURATION_URL=$(az network vnet-gateway vpn-client generate -g ${ARO_RESOURCE_GROUP_NAME} -n ${ARO_VGW_NAME} --processor-architecture Amd64)
echo "ARO_VGW_CONFIGURATION_URL=${ARO_VGW_CONFIGURATION_URL}"
```

